txt.en: Harlanc is located south of Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should enter the central building in the ruins at Harlanc.
Thurindol can be found in the keep at Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should return the Ranger supplies you recovered to Thurindol.

You hand the Ranger supplies to Thurindol.\n\n'These are indeed ours. We stored supplies down in the vaults of one of the last standing buildings in Harlanc. I did not think the Haradrim would bother exploring the ruins' interiors, let alone find our cache. You have done a great service to return the supplies. Though consisting mainly of rope and arrow heads, these are invaluable items to a Ranger. Thank you.'
Enter the centre structure at Harlanc
Harlanc is located south of Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should retrieve Ranger supplies from within the ruins at Harlanc.
Haradrim looters sift through the rubble looking for any treasures in these forgotten vaults

You notice some of the supplies being carried about are not from Harad as they carry the mark of the Rangers of Ithilien. You should find those who loot the Rangers' cache from within the ruins and return the supplies to Thurindol in Bâr Húrin.
Ranger supplies stored within the ruins of Harlanc should be confiscated and returned to Thurindol in Bâr Húrin.
Retrieve Ranger Supplies from within Harlanc
Harlanc is located south of Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should enter the central building in the ruins at Harlanc.
